imdb.plot outline: Even though it is her wedding day, Queenie is depressed. Nothing ever works out for her. She is forced to live in the ring of corruption her father has provided her with. Her identical twin Shiela on the other hand, lives for the thrill of corruption and greed and welcomes any opportunity for power and growth in the mob. Konstantine their father and head of the mob has found the perfect mate for his daughter. His right hand man Vlad. Even though Queenie hates him and Shiela lusts for him, the father knows better than to mess around with feelings of love when it comes to a marriage deal. Today, in the midst of the wedding. Someone on the outside of the Russian mob has found a very important list. It is The Sex Slave Cargo List with names, addresses dates and other info that could potentially save these girls - Who discovered this list? Noone other then Mathew Gold, a techie from a dot com company who hopelessly pines away for his first love, who was taken away from him in HS by the Russian Mob into sex slavery. I guess our only question now is, how will Matthew stop the Russian mob?
